title: Preseason winners & losers
itunes:title: Preseason winners & losers
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – analyze the latest news from around the league including the latest surrounding injuries to Jordy Nelson and Maurkice Pouncey and the QB battle in Houston. The guys then list their winners and losers from the second week of preseason.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
